<h1> Room name: <%= @room_name %></h1>
<h1> Player: <%= @player.name %></h1>

<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Player</th> 
            <th>Prohibited action</th>
            <th>Lives</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% @players.each do |player|%>
            <tr>
                <td><%= player.name %></td>
                <% if @player.id != player.id%>
                    <td><%= player.prohibited_action.name %></td>
                <% else %>
                    <td>*********  </td>
                <% end %>
                <td><%= player.lives %></td>
            </tr>
        <% end %>
    </tbody>
</table>
<h2><%= button_to 'I lost', player_path(@player.id), method: "patch" %></h2>
<br>
<h2> Game rule:</h2>
<p>1. Create a player for yourself and create a new room by leave the room field empty.</p>
<p>2. Other players join the room by type in the 7 characters room name which appears on the top of the screen once created.</p>
<p>3. On players screen, you can see remaining lives and others prohibited actions but not your own.</p>
<p>4. Start the game. Try to let other players do their prohibited action.</p>
<p>5. A player should react reasonably on others action. No response or no reaction which making the game boring is prohibited. </p>
<p>6. Those who did their prohibited action will lose one live by pressing "I lost". The player will be assigned a new prohibited action. </p>
<p>7. Other players reload the page to check the new prohibited action.</p>
<p>8. The first player lost all their lives is the loser and will recieve a punishment. Decide punishments with your group.</p>
<p>9. Have fun!</p>